track_notes: May be you can park at the small village Escragnoles, some times in summer it will be the Donkey Fest, avoid this period! the track is easy and not long. get some water in summertime. Plenty room for antenna

If you choose this track; park at the Galant Parking, many places, in summer get some water, plenty room on summit for antenna. On your way back you can visit the waterfall (cascade du Ray) and have a dive in very cold water!
